2:T6f8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is AIVA better than Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. AIVA scores 7.0 overall while Suno scores 8.0. AIVA is best for film and game composers and orchestral and classical music, while Suno excels for creating music without instruments and content creators needing custom music."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, AIVA or Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AIVA starts at $11/mo and Suno starts at $8/mo. AIVA offers a free plan. Suno offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from AIVA to Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both AIVA and Suno support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about AIVA vs Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, AIVA holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Suno has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 10/10. Users praise AIVA for excellent orchestral compositions and Suno for incredibly easy to use."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, AIVA or Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Suno for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, AIVA remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent orchestral compositions. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header"