6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AIVA and Suno share a solid foundation of core features including Music Generation. On the other hand, Suno uniquely offers Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AIVA holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Suno scores 8/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Suno comes in at a lower starting price of $8/mo, while AIVA begins at $11/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. AIVA's free tier and Suno's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
